</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سقوط-الاسنان?page=527" > Tooth Loss </a> of the front teeth without pain in a dream</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سقوط-الأسنان-في-المنام?page=3958" > Tooth Loss </a> of the front teeth in a dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-غير-المتزوجة-لابن-سيرين?page=786" > a single woman </a> indicates that she will lose something valuable to her soon, but she will not sleep on it.<br/>Also, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سقوط-الأسنان-في-المنام?page=3958" > Tooth Loss </a> of the front teeth in a dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-غير-المتزوجة-لابن-سيرين?page=786" > a single woman </a> indicates breaking off the engagement and the problems that will arise for her.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سقوط-الأسنان-في-المنام?page=3958" > Tooth Loss </a> in a dream for a married woman is an indication of the severance of the succession and the emergence of marital problems.</p>
<h2><span>Detailed interpretation of tooth loss in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Age: Teeth show family and relatives and may indicate property or secrets<br/>The falling out of a person's teeth in a dream means longevity without its counterpart in age<br/>If he sees that all his teeth have fallen out and he has taken them on his sleeve or in a room, then he will live a long time until his teeth fall out and the number of his household increases.<br/>And if he sees that all his teeth have fallen out and have gone from his sight, then his household will die before him, and this may be the death of his peers or the illness of his household.<br/>And if he sees that one of his teeth has been lost, then he will be far from his family, and if he hits it after losing it, he will return, otherwise he will not return.</p>
<p>Whoever sees his teeth falling into his hand, this is money that will come upon him, and if it falls into his lap, it is a child, and if it falls to the ground, then his misfortune is death.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
