</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>If a person sees that his lower teeth have fallen out, then he will suffer pain, sorrow, and torment<br/>Whoever is indebted, if his teeth fall out in a dream, this means that he will pay off his debt, and if he sees that a tooth has fallen out, then the man will pay off his debt or he will pay it in one lump sum.<br/>And if his teeth fall out, he will pay off several of his debtors, or one of them will spend a lot of things, and if his teeth fall out without pain, this indicates what he will invalidate.<br/>And if he sees that he is falling from pain, this indicates that something in his house and the openings of his teeth will vanish if they fall.<br/>If all the teeth fall out, then everyone in that house, both companions and single people and travelers, will perish, and this vision shows them a long illness without dying.</p>
<p>Whoever sees his teeth falling out while lifting them with his hand or his beard or his lap, this indicates that his children will be cut off and will not be born to him.</p>
<p>If a person dreams that his teeth have fallen out and he cannot eat, he will be poor<br/>Whoever sees him fall into his palm without pain and healing, he is a dirham after their number.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
