</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever sees his teeth falling out in his neck, and he takes them out tooth by tooth and places each tooth in its place, then his well's stones fall out, and he wants to take them out stone by stone and place each stone in its place. [p. 312] Thirty dinars, and it was said: If he had a well, it would collapse, and they said that he would become ill with a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-مرض-خطير?page=3508" > serious illness </a> , and his money will go to expenses, and someone else will benefit from his money.</p>
<p>If a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > person </a> sees that his teeth have receded, then he will pay off his debt slowly<br/>Whoever sees the topography of his teeth, his family will fail him when he needs them.</p>
<p>And whoever sees his teeth out of place and moving away from their rows, so that the upper ones are lower, and the lower ones are higher, this indicates that the women of his house will prolong their time on their men.<br/>Whoever sees a defect in his teeth, this indicates the scattering of his family or the appearance of a discrepancy among them, or a lack of his money, and if the flesh between his teeth is purified, then people will burn and humiliate him with his tongue.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
