</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>And it was said: Whoever sees his teeth falling out, he warns of evil with some of his friends, and if he sees the falling of a fold on his hand or tying it in his clothes, then the son or brother or sister will benefit.<br/>And if he sees that all his teeth have fallen out in his hand or with him, then the offspring of the people of this house will multiply and their number will increase, and one tooth will fall out if it is without treatment and he takes it.  in his hand or entwined in his clothes.<br/>And if there is blood, this is a sin for cutting off ties of kinship, unless he is in debt and is called upon to fulfill it, then he will deal with it.<br/>And it was said: That <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سقوط-الأسنان-في-المنام?page=3958" > Tooth Loss </a> indicates an obstacle that prevents him from what he wants, and it is said: Evidence of paying debts, and if he took what fell from his teeth, then perhaps he said. falsely and regretted it and hid it.  And perhaps the fine is like blood for the tooth in ...</p>
