<div class="entry-content clear" itemprop="text">
<div class="is-layout-constrained entry-content wp-block-post-content">
<div>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الزجاج-في-المنام?page=3314" > Seeing glass </a> in a dream means an arrogant person and other interpretations that we will explain for the single man, the married, the pregnant and the divorced, such as transparent glass or <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-كسر-الزجاج-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2935" > broken glass </a> colored or walking on broken glass according to al-Nabulsi, Imam Abdullah.  Honest and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> and others on:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of glass in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Glass in a dream and everything made from it shows arrogance, broken glass shows money, and transparent glass shows the wife or maid or other women.<br/>The abundance of mosques in the house is evidence of meeting women in good and evil.</p>
<p>It was said that glass in a vision is few and many of them, and whoever sees glass and something hidden from him is with him.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
