</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-كسر-الزجاج-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2935" > Broken glass </a> indicates hypocrites, meaning that you discover that there are people who are hypocritical towards you, while the bottle is a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-ظهر-المرأة-في-المنام-للنابلسي?page=1926" > woman’s appearance </a> that it does not hide, because the bottle reveals what is inside it.</p>
<p>Glass in a dream also shows anxiety, and whoever sees glass in his dream while something or a secret is hidden from him, this means that it will be seen and become clear to him because glass does not hide anything.<br/>As for seeing everything through colored glass in a dream, this indicates suspicions of money, spouses, and children, and indicates hypocrisy and hypocrisy.<br/>And what is used for the benefit of man, such as glasses and glass in a dream, is evidence of scholars and wise men.</p>
<p>And whoever sells glass in a dream indicates that he has chosen the world over the hereafter, or sin over obedience, or the apostate from his religion.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
	atOptions = {
		'key' : '472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d',
