</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الزجاج-في-المنام?page=3314" > Seeing glass </a> in a dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/مترجم-الأحلام-محمد-بن-سيرين?page=3415" > Dream interpreter Muhammad ibn Sirin </a> mentioned that <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الزجاج-في-المنام?page=3314" > seeing glass </a> in a dream indicates the anxiety and sadness that will remain present in the dreamer’s life, and depending on the amount of the glass, the amount of sadness will be.  Leave soon.</p>
<p>If <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-زجاج-في-المنام?page=2944" > seeing glass </a> is healthy in a dream, it means that the problems will not end and it is proven that they will continue for a while.</p>
<p>If the glass is green in color in a dream, it indicates the worships that the servant receives, and red glass shows love that ends in evil, while yellow glass shows a passing illness.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
	atOptions = {
		'key' : '472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d',
		'format' : 'iframe',
		'height' : 250,
		'width' : 300,
		'params' : {}
	};
	document.write('<scr' + 'ipt type="text/javascript" src="http' + (location.protocol === 'https:' ? 's' : '') + '://tinyplywood.com/472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d/invoke.js"></scr' + 'ipt>');
</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>If a person looks through the glass in a dream, this indicates that there will be some serious disappointments that will overshadow his life and hopes.</p>
<p>If a married woman sees a silhouette in the glass mirror, this indicates her husband’s neglect, and it may indicate her husband’s betrayal of her.</p>
<p>If you look in the mirror and see another face with your face, this indicates that you are living a double life, and it indicates that you are a deceitful person who deceives many friends.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
	atOptions = {
		'key' : '472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d',
		'format' : 'iframe',
		'height' : 250,
