</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>When seeing seven cows in a dream, interpreters agree on interpreting this dream as an indication of seven years of life in a state of prosperity and progress.  Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/قطيع-من-الأبقار-في-المنام?page=3226" > herd of cows </a> is an indication that the dreamer will find the person who inhabits his heart with him and he will find many good days with him.  He will achieve great and wonderful successes in his life.  He will reach the highest degrees and reach the highest positions.</p>
<p>Many cows in a dream are evidence of reaching strength, prestige, pride, and dignity.  As for those who have suffered from severe anxiety in their lives, the dream warns of the disappearance of sorrow and anxiety and the improvement of life in general. level.</p>
<h2><strong>Interpretation of the Dream of Cows by <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></strong></h2>
<p>The respected scholar <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> stated that seeing many cows in a dream means that years of luck and fortune await us.  In the event of seeing many cows, this is an indication of attachment to religious teachings. The dreamer also symbolizes the achievement of all aspirations.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
