</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>And Muhammad Ibn Sirin confirmed that many cows indicate reaching authority and high positions.  As for those suffering from a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-مرض-خطير?page=3508" > serious illness </a>, the dream warns of recovery from the disease and illness and the return of health and well-being once again.  Seeing many cows of different colors was a sign of fluctuations in circumstances.</p>
<h2><strong>Interpretation of the Dream of a Cow for a Single Woman</strong></h2>
<p>Legal interpreters say that <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الأب-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3719" > seeing a father </a>cow in a dream for an unmarried woman is a good omen that her marriage is approaching a good man who will give her feelings of love and anxiety.  Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-بقرة-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين-والنابلسي?page=4066" > white cow </a> in the dream of an unmarried woman is evidence that her life will improve a lot and she will achieve many goals and ambitions that she has long aspired to.</p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الأب-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3719" > lean father </a>cow in the dream of an unmarried woman is evidence of her marriage to a poor man who is not in good health and she will live with him in a state of hardship and poverty.  Many obstacles in her life.  But if the cows are thin, it indicates a delay in her marriage.  Seeing many white cows in a dream is an indication that there will be a formal engagement soon.  The dream also carries good news for her.  To get a suitable job with a high salary that will help her improve many aspects of her life.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
