<h2><strong>Interpretation of a Dream of Many Cows for a Married Woman</strong></h2>
<p>Seeing many cows in the dream of a married woman indicates that she wants to perform the required duties of her as well as possible.  But if the cows are fat, it means that she will live a very happy, comfortable, and stable life with her children.  Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الأب-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3719" > father </a>cow is a sign that the dreamer will be able to overcome all the problems and crises that she will go through.</p>
<p>Seeing many cows in the dream of a married woman is evidence that she is going through a very difficult time at the moment and cannot cope with it.  It is important not to give up her prayers because God can change all circumstances in the blink of an eye. If the married woman sees that she is going to the market to buy cows, this indicates, on condition that her husband finds a new job.  Or a new promotion in his higher-paying job.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
